---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Études Environnementales & Publications"
description: "Expertise technique sur les conventions BRS, Minamata, CCNUCC et SAICM en République du Congo."
keywords: "études environnementales Congo, conventions BRS, mercure Congo, climat Congo, expertise écologique"
---

<section class="page-banner">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="page-banner-content">
            <h1>Nos Travaux d'Études</h1>
            <p><span class="highlight">À ce jour l'AED, a contribué à la mise en œuvre au Congo des publications et recherches sur les conventions environnementales.</span></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

{% include "partners-banner.html" %}

<div class="main">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="layout">
            <aside class="sidebar">
                <h3>Conventions</h3>
                <ul id="conventionsList">
                    {% for slug, convention in studies %}
                    <li>
                        <button class="conv-btn {% if loop.first %}active{% endif %}" data-conv="{{ slug }}" onclick="showConvention('{{ slug }}')">
                            {{ convention.icon }} {{ convention.title }}
                        </button>
                    </li>
                    {% endfor %}
                </ul>
            </aside>
            <div class="content" id="content">
                {% for slug, convention in studies %}
                <div id="conv-{{ slug }}" class="convention-section {% if loop.first %}active{% else %}hidden{% endif %}">
                    <div class="content-header">
                        <h2>{{ convention.title }}</h2>
                        <p>{{ convention.subtitle }}</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="studies-list">
                        {% for study in convention.studies %}
                        <article class="study-card">
                            <div class="study-header">
                                <span class="study-year">{{ study.year }}</span>
                                <span class="study-status status-{{ study.status }}">
                                    {% if study.status == 'published' %}✓ Publié{% elif study.status == 'progress' %}⚙️ En cours{% else %}📅 À venir{% endif %}
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <h3>{{ study.title }}</h3>
                            <p class="study-desc">{{ study.desc }}</p>
                            <div class="study-meta">
                                <strong>Auteurs :</strong> {{ study.authors }}
                            </div>
                            <div class="study-tags">
                                {% for tag in study.tags %}
                                <span class="tag">{{ tag }}</span>
                                {% endfor %}
                            </div>
                        </article>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .hidden { display: none; }
    .convention-section.active { display: block; }
    .conv-btn { 
        width: 100%; text-align: left; background: none; border: none; 
        padding: 12px 15px; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 6px;
        color: var(--text-secondary); transition: all 0.2s;
        font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px;
    }
    .conv-btn:hover { background: var(--bg-green-pale); color: var(--primary); }
    .conv-btn.active { background: var(--secondary); color: white; }
    
    .study-card { 
        background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); 
        border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px;
        transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .study-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); }
    .study-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .study-year { font-weight: 700; color: var(--secondary); }
    .study-status { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 20px; }
    .status-published { background: #e6f4ea; color: #1e7e34; }
    .status-progress { background: #fff4e5; color: #b45d00; }
    .study-card h3 { font-family: 'Lora', serif; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .study-desc { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .study-meta { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .study-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
    .tag { background: var(--bg-light); color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 11px; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
</style>

{% set scripts %}
<script src="/js/studies.js"></script>
{% endset %}